<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Prag</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Konrad Molitor, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen der Forderungen an Nürnberger und auswärtige Kaufleute in Prag an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_57" id="28v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_57_r2l19">Der <expan>Gröſʒ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Stat ʒu Prag </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_57_r2l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> wır <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> / vvıe daʒ Jr ettlıch mutung getan habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l21">an vnſer vnd auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> kawffleẅt dıe denn Jren <expan>gew<ex>er</ex>b</expan> bey eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l22"><expan>treıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Mollıtor <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l23"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> / Dem wır befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawffleẅt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l24">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . mıt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> dauon ʒe reden . Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l27">eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ . / VVas derſelb vnſer 
<add><ab facs="#facs_57_line_1576668070615_2691"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd </ab></add> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l28">dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> darumb an eẅch werbe / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l29">Jm des <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd gütlıch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>auſrıcht<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l30">von eẅch <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet / vnd darinn vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_57_r2l31">eẅr <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweıſet als wır ein </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_58" id="29r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_58_r1l2"><expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> gut getrawn ʒu eẅch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Vnd eẅch vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_58_r1l3">auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vmb eẅr <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> allcʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_58_r1l5"><expan>wıllıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_58_r1l4"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_57" id="28v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der <expan>grösz<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stat zu Prag </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie daz ir ettlich mutung getan
                        habt an unser und auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> kawfflewt, die denn
                        iren <expan>gew<ex>er</ex>b</expan> bey ewch
                        <expan>treibe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Mollitor, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>dien<ex>er,</ex></expan> dem wir
                        befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        kawfflewt und der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> davon ze reden, und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, was derselb unser
                                    <add><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und</add>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> darumb an ewch werbe, daz ir im des
                                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und gütlich <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ausricht<ex>en</ex></expan> und von ewch
                            <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet und darinn uns und den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewr
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweiset, als wir ein <pb facs="#facs_58" id="29r"/><expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan> gut getrawn zu ewch
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ewch und den
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey uns auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        tun <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        umb ewr <expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> allczeit
                                <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
